  "gloss": "Statement of record: `Eidometry.Thesis.dyadic_base` (Eidometry thesis, section Executed runs).\n\nEvery finite executed IEEE-754 float32 value, read as a real number, is exactly a dyadic rational (an integer divided by a power of two). This is the bridge that makes executed floating-point arithmetic exact mathematics rather than an approximation.\n\nDischarged by [MTH.R-2026-1201].\n",
